com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.directions

Class DirectionsResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.directions.DirectionsResponse

  • public class DirectionsResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstraction of a response from the directions route of ORS API. It might have the ascent, descent and average speed of the route. You must check it before using the fields.
    Author:
    Marcos Henrique
